WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:18.380
December ,1941. Thailand and Japan become allies

00:00:23.180 --> 00:00:26.740
Donmuang Airport

00:01:16.780 --> 00:01:20.320
November 29, 1944

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:23.280
More than 50 B-29 SuperFortress was ordered

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:25.040
To began a huge air raid on Thailand

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:27.680
7 Thai Ki-43 was ordered to intercept them (with 14 IJA fighter)

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:05.820
One B-29 was damaged by Ki-43 of Flt. Lt.Therdsak  Worrasap

00:02:05.820 --> 00:02:07.600
And was down in the bay of Bengal

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:09.520
Flt. Lt. Therdsak plane was burn down by return fire

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:11.400
He decided to bail out

